name: Vegan Frogs from Outer Space
description:
VEGAN FROGS FROM OUTER SPACE

Made for Frog Jam in 72 hours.

One frog takes the leap to become a vegan after some convincing from an airborne friend.

Game programmed with love from scratch using no libraries or engines - only raw JS, HTML and a bit of CSS.
